  "Charles Edelstenne has spent more than 50 years working at French firm Dassault. ",
  "A qualified accountant, Edelstenne started working at Dassault Aviation in 1960 as head of the financial studies department.",
  "The Parisian businessman cofounded Dassault Systèmes, the aviation giant's software and consulting arm, in 1981. ",
  "He was tapped as the group's vice chairman five years later.",
  "Edelstenne remains chairman of the board of Dassault Systèmes; he and his family own around 6% of Dassault Systèmes' capital.  "
